{"tid":340304,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[年經]HKUST 科大reg day+Ocamp攻略","createTime":"2017-07-29T19:49:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T05:42:18.000Z","uid":32419,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"69570381203ca11044bd61899a134585cb2c2f42","tid":340304,"uid":32419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T19:49:24.000Z","msg":"未放榜又擺咗UST係jupas ge你依家做緊咩呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前見到某藍色busi soc開哂名出post收member<br />\n希望呢個post真係俾到d諗住玩吓ocamp識下frd ge巴絲打少少advice la<br />\n如果有咩問題就問la,其他巴絲打見到小弟有咩打錯都可以幫手補充嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Reg day</span></span><br />\n作為一個UST freshman<br />\n一定會經歷清水灣大學既Reg Day<br />\n呢個除咗係唯一一個日子可以比女圍住既好日子之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實都有正經野要做ge<br />\nBTW今年su改咗reg day個名做welcoming fair,係9/8-10/8<br />\n其實同以前reg day差唔多,個日記住去CYT building攞學生證同activate itsc就ok<br />\n得閒ge就攞住新嘅學生證去吓liba(即係library)9fing下,或者試下LG7啲野食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Ocamp</span></span><br />\n科大傳說有淫game又可以抽下女水，放心其實咩人型蜈蚣同生命麵包係乜都無(除非有,都市傳說有個<span style=\"color: green;\">綠色hall</span>曾經出現過,freshmen可以自己睇蘋果動個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )。<br />\n你地係絕對無可能光明正大咁抽人水架。絲打們都唔洗擔心架，可以安心玩Ocamp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今年ocamp ge日期係&nbsp;<br />\n12-14/8 ICA, ACC, SA, HSSU&nbsp;<br />\n14-16/8 Science dept soc, IPO soc<br />\n16-18/8 Engin dept soc, BSU<br />\n19-21/8 Busi dep soc, ESU&nbsp;<br />\n21-24/8 Hall <br />\n<br />\n科大有百幾個soc,巴絲打一入嚟一定搞唔清邊個soc ocamp先啱自己<br />\n咁就首先分下類la<br />\n科大ge soc主要分做School, Department ,興趣soc同Hall<br />\n基本上好多soc都係under su, su今年唔知有冇ocamp,就算有都應該冇咩人會玩,因為呢幾年佢地都冇搞ocamp<br />\n<br />\n School既Ocamp就分為<br />\nThe Business Students' Union&nbsp;(BSU) (專俾讀business ge freshmen玩)<br />\nThe Engineering Students' Union&nbsp;(ESU) (專俾讀engineering ge freshmen玩)<br />\nThe Humanities and Social Science Students' Union&nbsp;(HSSU) (專俾讀social science ge freshmen玩)<br />\nScience Students' Union&nbsp;(SSU) (專俾讀science ge freshmen玩)<br />\nInterdisciplinary Programs Students&rsquo; Union (IPSU) (專俾讀IPO ge freshmen玩)<br />\n通常就玩番自己個School就ok架啦<br />\nSchool搞既Ocamp姐係其他u既大O，好多freshmen一齊玩，好易識到好多人，不過因為多人玩所以比較難同人熟啲，多數都係hi-bye fd<br />\n如果想識多啲人都可以玩，唔玩都無損失既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有SSU同IPSU呢幾年都好似冇搞ocamp<br />\n所以比較出名都係BSU, ESU同HSSU呢D school ocamp <br />\n<br />\nDepartment soc ge ocamp就比school ge ocamp好玩好多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n好多freshmen都會跟自己讀或者想讀既major而去玩個個soc<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁做絕對係錯誤既選擇</span> 如果黎緊想識啲朋友一齊玩一齊做下project就要小心揀dept soc既ocamp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由於小弟係隻busi狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁就介紹下busi soc ocamp先la<br />\n科大最出名ge busi department soc就係一定係兩大紅色soc<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">MSA</span> 就sell warm and caring <br />\n同時間專搵名校靚仔靚女玩,顏值都有咁上下保證<br />\n以往搞既ocamp都好玩架，又有真火campfire同水戰嗰d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過既然搵得名校,就一定比較小圈子,所以識都係識d hi-bye frd<br />\n仲有絲打就要好好照顧自己,毛毛蟲呢隻game係MSA都幾出名下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知今年又搞成點呢?<br />\n另外一個紅色大soc就係<span style=\"color: red;\">ECON</span><br />\n佢既賣點係sell 團結同家庭feel<br />\n組爸媽都幾照顧freshman,又有beach day又有campfire同bbq<br />\n靚仔靚女數量同MSA差唔多,freshmen裏面都冇咩搞小圈子<br />\n不過MSA唔同ge就係冇真火campfire同埋少d名校撚<br />\n仲有有時會chur下班freshmen玩下唔同game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有興趣接觸多啲人(同埋試吓出pool)可以報吓呢兩個紅色soc ge ocamp <br />\n仲有<span style=\"color: blue;\">Acct soc</span>，好多major咗accounting嘅freshmen都會玩<br />\n一定冇咁chur因為聽講準時訓覺準時起身,應該參考咗各種中學camp<br />\n不過就比較悶,因為有會計師公會sponsor，要聽埋啲無聊talk<br />\n所以好唔好玩就見人見智啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Fina soc</span>就年年都出動佢地個招牌女神exxxx chow去reg人<br />\n不過可惜，佢應該都唔會再出現係ocamp (好似就grad)<br />\n所以唔好比佢呃到<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">Isom soc</span> 好多都係on campus既game 同埋啲組爸媽都幾nice架<br />\n不過就比較摺 小人玩啲<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">Marketing soc</span>今年好似有zone制 不過近年就愈黎愈小聲氣<br />\n不過啲人都幾玩得 想試下新野ge巴絲打都可以玩下<br />\n<br />\n至於engine soc 同science soc方面<br />\ncivil同mech呢兩個係比較多engine freshmen玩ge camp<br />\n特別係civil,因為civil係比較搶手d ge major, 組爸媽好多都係civil major<br />\n所以都可能有啲用<br />\nchem同bich都係多science freshmen報ge ocamp<br />\n巴絲打可以跟返自已心水ge ocamp<br />\n方便第日上堂同一齊玩<br />\n<br />\nHall ge ocamp有興趣知遲啲再講"},{"pid":"416bad7e02acf38e6f69b2df52975b699f4326af","tid":340304,"uid":5889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T02:23:17.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48330c37a8d6c60a12ead3d5203735b6fb290f57","tid":340304,"uid":46320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T02:54:41.000Z","msg":"msa今年唔係收左皮咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n難分真與假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd62b7f2d548c1ef7a918a1037e7d95b421e964","tid":340304,"uid":81414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:41:20.000Z","msg":"唔介紹IPO<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e86d952709acd660acb4e4b310e6a67ec100d3","tid":340304,"uid":1788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:57:32.000Z","msg":"放心啦FM們<br />\n極多情況你都係識到d hi-bye friend<br />\n或者連hi-bye都無既friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e85f2e6f92344506f5322de1b5941f436218b17","tid":340304,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:57:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>msa今年唔係收左皮咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n難分真與假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b711200db2f64805ab95df272326b0a3ad3d058","tid":340304,"uid":21964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:59:59.000Z","msg":"又係到吹奏ocamp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86566ecf32faaf877edc6493bbb5ed38477e4f2d","tid":340304,"uid":6093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:01:36.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"3360de41a26ee1c01d1a6c9ac6cd4ad72498bf91","tid":340304,"uid":40826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:11:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔介紹IPO<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n入得IPO既就知呢啲打手文係唔洗睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋有IPSU就夠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7845a9aa7f59dd7704d85ac62a565c5269e503a5","tid":340304,"uid":78166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:12:51.000Z","msg":"沉底都比你班友推返上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b817cd7475b32a08da1c782c12c348142589c74c","tid":340304,"uid":78166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:13:42.000Z","msg":"econ紙皮打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571f37a8e1b32b21a346ff469e800fe9c323f705","tid":340304,"uid":84128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:14:53.000Z","msg":"個camp用紙皮砌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7232dea4422f02d00d9d0b05e807c8c10fc70cd7","tid":340304,"uid":128095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:36:49.000Z","msg":"今年Msa Pro P柒到冇眼睇 狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81facfa49643cc0d0b8922a2c4c806bbe3d3f345","tid":340304,"uid":4238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:42:18.000Z","msg":"由得佢沉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打手post"}]}